何人藉任何作為或不作為假冒公職人員，或假裝能促致公職人員作出或不作出與其職責有關的任何作為或事情，不論是否意圖取得任何有價值的東西，均可處罰款$1,000或監禁6個月。」"},{"pid":"6e5ea93aa93ed3bf24fc4ee2592f8c30507d0ac3","tid":1229900,"uid":25598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"無委任證分分鐘係啲廢青搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee96655c44a185bf05bd7db49a813f2ad28d0333","tid":1229900,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"全民淘背心"},{"pid":"b9480a599b2eac6d5c69de8d6d0146e393dd086e","tid":1229900,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"你知唔知有個牌子哪POLICE 架"},{"pid":"9c64d3ad19d1e23e3bd3e231ee0d752e18837f92","tid":1229900,"uid":28435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"05d382fe6fd3ddbb5085b0a526d6e7874fb63960","tid":1229900,"uid":32511,"like":467,"dislike":6,"score":461,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"其實俾唔出證，市民可唔可以行駛市民權力，暫時制服佢，再打999交冒警者俾可以出示委任證嘅警察？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"理論上可以，但對家「全都是我的人」黑哨慣，都係你輸硬"},{"pid":"bcff0ccb9b1d6b5d3a31f92da448fc0d164781bd","tid":1229900,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9480a599b2eac6d5c69de8d6d0146e393dd086e","tid":1229900,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"你知唔知有個牌子哪POLICE 架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"你知唔知有個牌子叫* POLICE 架"},{"pid":"e7522a7eceaa8ca953dfaaed04fa8f03719021a8","tid":1229900,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee96655c44a185bf05bd7db49a813f2ad28d0333","tid":1229900,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"全民淘背心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"發夢見到成條街都冒警噉遊行，痴撚線，犯法㗎冒警！點知原來只係一件黑色背心，之後我就瞓醒咗啦"},{"pid":"5a713312b9d2e2b6bcc5062f46494409b95df2d3","tid":1229900,"uid":15336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote"